      FREE ROOF INSPECTION<br/><span class="gt">ST. PETERSBURG, FL</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="max-w-2xl mx-auto" style="color:#555555;font-size:1.05rem;line-height:1.75">
      Schedule a free, no-obligation roof inspection in St. Petersburg with Happy Roof. Our licensed inspectors examine every layer of your roofing system and provide a detailed report with photos, so you know exactly what shape your roof is in.
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 justify-center mt-8">
      <a href="/contact" class="btn-t">Get a Free Estimate <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg></a>
      <a href="tel:8135957663" class="btn-o call-tracking-number">Call (813) 595-7663</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- INFO STRIP -->
<div style="background:#FFFFFF;border-top:2px solid #E6A817;border-bottom:1px solid #E0E0E0;padding:.85rem 0">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-5">
    <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-8 gap-y-2 font-display font-bold text-sm tracking-widest" style="color:#1A1A1A;text-transform:uppercase;font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif">
      <span>St. Petersburg, FL</span><span style="color:#E6A817">·</span><span>CCC1337380</span><span style="color:#E6A817">·</span><span>HappyRoof.com</span><span style="color:#E6A817">·</span><span style="color:#3B9FD9">(813) 595-7663</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- WHY SECTION -->
<section class="py-20" style="background:#FFFFFF">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-5">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-14 items-start">
      <div>
        <p class="sl gt mb-3">Why Get a Free Inspection</p>
        <h2 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem);line-height:.95;color:#1A1A1A;letter-spacing:-.01em;margin-bottom:1.5rem">WHY ST. PETERSBURG HOMEOWNERS SCHEDULE ROOF INSPECTIONS</h2>
        <p style="color:#555555;font-size:1rem;line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:1.5rem">St. Petersburg's coastal location on the Pinellas peninsula subjects roofs to a uniquely aggressive combination of salt air, intense UV radiation, and some of the highest annual rainfall totals in Florida. Many homeowners in neighborhoods like Jungle Terrace, Riviera Bay, and Crescent Lake own mid-century homes with roofs that are 15 to 25 years old - approaching or past their expected lifespan. Without a professional inspection, hidden deterioration can go unnoticed until a storm exposes it as a major leak.</p>
        <p style="color:#555555;font-size:1rem;line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:1.5rem">A roof inspection is especially important in St. Petersburg before hurricane season, after any major storm, or if you are buying or selling a home. Insurance companies in Florida increasingly require roof condition reports for policy renewals, and having a documented inspection from a licensed contractor gives you a clear picture of where your roof stands. Homes in Shore Acres and Coquina Key, which sit at lower elevations near the bay, face additional risk from wind-driven rain that can exploit even small vulnerabilities.</p>
        <p style="color:#555555;font-size:1rem;line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:1.5rem">Happy Roof's inspections are genuinely free - no hidden fees, no obligation, and no sales pressure. We inspect, document, and report. If your roof is solid, we tell you. If there are issues, we explain your options clearly. Learn more about our presence in the area on our <a href="/st-petersburg-roofing" style="color:#3B9FD9;text-decoration:none;font-weight:600">St. Petersburg roofing page</a>.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="scard p-6">
          <div class="check"><div class="check-dot"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E6A817" stroke-width="3"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg></div><div><strong style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:1.05rem">Comprehensive 25-Point Check</strong><p style="color:#555555;font-size:.9rem;line-height:1.6;margin-top:.25rem">Every component inspected: surface material, flashing, ridge caps, valleys, drip edge, gutters, soffit, fascia, ventilation, and visible attic and decking condition.</p></div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="scard p-6">
          <div class="check"><div class="check-dot"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E6A817" stroke-width="3"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg></div><div><strong style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:1.05rem">Detailed Photo Documentation</strong><p style="color:#555555;font-size:.9rem;line-height:1.6;margin-top:.25rem">We photograph every finding - good and bad - so you can see your roof's condition in detail. Photos are included in your written report.</p></div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="scard p-6">
          <div class="check"><div class="check-dot"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E6A817" stroke-width="3"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg></div><div><strong style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:1.05rem">Written Report & Options</strong><p style="color:#555555;font-size:.9rem;line-height:1.6;margin-top:.25rem">Clear, jargon-free written report. If work is needed, we provide transparent estimates with material choices and pricing.</p></div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="scard p-6">
          <div class="check"><div class="check-dot"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E6A817" stroke-width="3"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg></div><div><strong style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:1.05rem">Zero Obligation</strong><p style="color:#555555;font-size:.9rem;line-height:1.6;margin-top:.25rem">No purchase required, no pressure. Our goal is to give St. Petersburg homeowners the information they need to make smart decisions about their roof.</p></div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- WHAT'S INCLUDED / COMMON REPAIRS / WHAT WE CHECK -->
<section class="py-20" style="background:#F7F7F7">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-5">
