      <p style="color:#555555;font-size:1rem;line-height:1.75;max-width:700px;margin:0 auto">Happy Roof provides free roof inspections throughout St. Petersburg and Pinellas County.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 md:grid-cols-4 lg:grid-cols-5 gap-3 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
